### Welcome to **Mohamed's** GitHub Pages.

### About Mohamed
I'm a fourth semester student at Ranken Tech. College.
My major is Internet Web Based Technology.
I graduate on May, 2016.

### View Mohamed's Portfolio!
You can view my portfolio, resume, skills, and some of the websites I've been working on at_ [Mohamed_Alkurwi_Portfolio](http://iwt.ranken.edu/malkurwi/).
